                supported by reliable service, comfortable surroundings, and attention to detail.
              </p>
              <p>
                Our goal is to build long-term relationships with our customers by consistently providing
                meals they can trust and enjoy. We strive to create a dining experience that is not only
                satisfying but also dependable, where guests feel valued and welcomed every time they visit.
              </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Right Image -->
